What you need to know:

With the experience of playing in Sweden, China and Spain's top-flight leagues in the past six years, Duhail SC reportedly fancy Olunga as an upgrade to former Bayern Munich striker Mario Mandzukic, who has failed to find the goals.Currently ranked third in Qatar's 12-team top flight, Duhail owner Abdullah bin Nasser bin Al Ahmed Al Thani has promised Olunga a 100 percent increase to his current Sh8 million monthly salary.